<p>Putting two community reps that can decide nothing on their own ISN'T listening. It's just throwing a bait. We know better. Thanks.</p>

<p>Some devs are truelly active at communicating but not that many and not about class balance most of the time.</p>

<p>Some love to shoot down bias. This is indeed a good place to do so.</p>
