<p>I don't consider having items on top ten lists "currently being evaluated" for 6 months as listening, answering, or shooting down anything. That's called stonewalling.</p>

<p>"Yes, numbers have been low, although anyone who tells you they have real data to support specific trends is most likely lying. Nothing tells us that we won't see the continued trend of new players joining in and old players returning..."</p>

