<p>Its the way that myself, and a few people I know, felt.  I only posted to see if any others felt the same.  </p>

<p>In a nutshell, I wasnt being melodramatic.</p>
<p class="posted"><strong>Posted by Redcloud at December 26, 2004 02:41 PM</strong></p>
<p>I can relate to that. The overall feeling I have is that people felt cheated by SoE when they had to sit outside of single group content because they couldn't add sufficient value. Be it in single group content or by the major shortcomings and changes of the raid content, people felt cheated by an order of magnitude compared to any previous expansion.</p>

